---
import OpportunityPage from '../../layouts/OpportunityPage.astro';
---

<OpportunityPage
	title="Opportunities for UCSD Students"
	description="Get involved with our lab through fellowships, events, and volunteer opportunities that complement your academic experience."
	pubDate={new Date('January 01 2023')}
	heroImage={undefined}
>
	<div class="content-page">
		<header class="page-header">
			<h1>Opportunities for UCSD Students</h1>
			<p class="page-description">
				Get involved with our lab through fellowships, events, and volunteer opportunities that complement your academic experience.
			</p>
		</header>

		<section class="content-section">
			<p class="lead-text">
				Get involved with our lab through fellowships, events, and volunteer opportunities that complement your academic experience.
			</p>
			
			<div class="opportunity-list">
				<div class="opportunity-item">
					<h3>Lab Fellows</h3>
					<p>Paid positions for students to contribute to our educational mission while developing technical skills, teaching experience, and leadership abilities. Fellows help design and deliver our programs.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="opportunity-item">
					<h3>Robot Teddy Bear Army Scavenger Hunt</h3>
					<p>Join our flagship annual event where teams navigate campus solving challenges with custom-built robot teddy bears. This fun competition showcases robotics skills and creative problem-solving.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="opportunity-item">
					<h3>Volunteer Opportunities</h3>
					<p>Contribute your time and skills to support our workshops, events, and outreach programs. Volunteers gain valuable experience while helping inspire the next generation of engineers.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="content-section">
			<h2>Lab Fellows Program</h2>
			<p>Our flagship program for UCSD students looking to make an impact:</p>
			
			<div class="opportunity-list">
				<div class="opportunity-item">
					<h3>Program Overview</h3>
					<p>Lab Fellows work 10-15 hours per week during academic quarters, developing educational content, mentoring K-12 students, and supporting our outreach events.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="opportunity-item">
					<h3>Benefits</h3>
					<p>Fellows receive competitive compensation, professional development opportunities, teaching experience, and the chance to build their technical portfolio while making a difference.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="opportunity-item">
					<h3>Application Process</h3>
					<p>Applications are accepted at the beginning of each quarter. Look for information sessions in week 1 of each quarter to learn more about the program and application requirements.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="content-section">
			<h2>Events & Competitions</h2>
			<p>Join our exciting events throughout the year:</p>
			
			<div class="opportunity-list">
				<div class="opportunity-item">
					<h3>Robot Teddy Bear Army Scavenger Hunt</h3>
					<p>Our annual campus-wide competition where teams build and program robot teddy bears to complete challenges across campus. Open to all UCSD students regardless of technical background.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="opportunity-item">
					<h3>Robotics Showcase</h3>
					<p>Quarterly events where students can demonstrate their robotics projects, network with industry professionals, and compete for prizes in various categories.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="opportunity-item">
					<h3>Workshop Series</h3>
					<p>Hands-on workshops covering topics from basic electronics to advanced machine learning, designed to complement your coursework and provide practical experience.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="content-section">
			<h2>Volunteer Opportunities</h2>
			<p>Ways to get involved with flexible time commitments:</p>
			
			<div class="opportunity-list">
				<div class="opportunity-item">
					<h3>K-12 Workshop Support</h3>
					<p>Help facilitate our weekend workshops for K-12 students. No prior experience needed - we'll provide training and all necessary materials.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="opportunity-item">
					<h3>Event Staffing</h3>
					<p>Support our larger events like the Robot Teddy Bear Army Scavenger Hunt, helping with setup, check-in, and activity facilitation.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="opportunity-item">
					<h3>Content Development</h3>
					<p>Help create educational materials, tutorials, and documentation for our robotics projects. Perfect for students interested in technical writing and curriculum design.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="content-section">
			<h2>Getting Started</h2>
			<p>How to get involved with our lab:</p>
			
			<div class="opportunity-list">
				<div class="opportunity-item">
					<h3>1. Attend an Info Session</h3>
					<p>Join our quarterly information sessions to learn about all available opportunities and meet current lab members.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="opportunity-item">
					<h3>2. Complete Interest Form</h3>
					<p>Fill out our online interest form to let us know about your background, skills, and what opportunities interest you most.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="opportunity-item">
					<h3>3. Join Our Community</h3>
					<p>Connect with us through our mailing list, Discord server, and social media to stay updated on new opportunities and events.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="content-section">
			<h2>Student Testimonials</h2>
			<p>What UCSD students are saying about their experience:</p>
			
			<div class="opportunity-list">
				<div class="opportunity-item">
					<h3>"The Lab Fellows program transformed my UCSD experience"</h3>
					<p>"Working as a Lab Fellow gave me practical teaching experience, technical skills I couldn't get in my classes, and connections that led to my internship."</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="opportunity-item">
					<h3>"The Robot Teddy Bear Hunt was unforgettable"</h3>
					<p>"I had no robotics experience but joined the competition anyway. Our team didn't win, but I learned so much and made friends I still have today."</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="opportunity-item">
					<h3>"Volunteering opened new career paths"</h3>
					<p>"I started volunteering to help with workshops and discovered I love teaching. Now I'm pursuing a career in educational technology."</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>

	<style>
		.opportunity-list {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 1.5rem;
			margin-top: 2rem;
		}

		.opportunity-item {
			padding: 1.5rem;
			background: rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.05);
			border-radius: 12px;
			border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent), 0.1);
			transition: all 0.3s ease;
		}

		.opportunity-item:hover {
			transform: translateY(-2px);
			box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(var(--accent), 0.1);
			background: rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.1);
		}

		.opportunity-item h3 {
			margin-top: 0;
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
			font-size: 1.25rem;
			color: var(--accent);
		}

		.opportunity-item p {
			margin-bottom: 0;
			font-size: 1rem;
		}
	</style>
</OpportunityPage>